data.description: Nestled in the heart of a charming neighborhood, this modified 2-Story home offers the tranquility of suburban life with easy access to city amenities, schools, parks, and more. This home features generously sized living spaces, including a cozy family room with fireplace, spacious kitchen with stainless steel appliances, and 4 bedrooms. Step outside into your own private backyard, which is a haven for relaxation. It features an entertainment-size deck & patio, lush landscaping, and room for your own garden or outdoor entertainment.
